text.tspan: Did you deviate from the rules? Where? How did that go?
How many points in the Good Bank? Did you use them?
How many points in the Bad Bank? Did you use them?
Did the players seek out, or avoid combat?
Did you calculate "party power" and "foe power" before combat?
Did the campaign rules work for you?
Did play ever grind to a halt?
